### Writing Style

* Use US spelling and grammar.
* Direct, simp writing style.
* Avoid long and complex words and grammar.
* Use acronums only if they are commonly understood.
* Use "and" instead of "&".
* Use words instead of numbers (from one to ten).

### Body

* Break long sentences into smaller, shorter ones.

